Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.84,0:03:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.14,0:03:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can you possibly be planning, Yagami Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:04:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By touching a Death Note that you previously owned, all your memories associated with it will be recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.42,0:04:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's a Shinigami... {\alpha&HFF&}they really do... exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.96,0:04:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's a Shinigami... they really do... {\alpha&HFF&}exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's a Shinigami... they really do... exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.94,0:04:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.69,0:04:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Showed each other our notebooks in Aoyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love at first sight...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.95,0:04:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, give me the notebook!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.22,0:04:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira's method of killing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.62,0:04:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira... the second Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two notebooks...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.06,0:04:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More than one notebook exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.18,0:04:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not over yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.72,0:05:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am L...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.15,0:05:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am L...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.32,0:05:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-{\alpha&HFF&}Are you okay? Anyone would be petrified if they saw that monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you okay? {\alpha&HFF&}Anyone would be petrified if they saw that monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you okay? Anyone would be petrified if they saw that monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.69,0:05:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.95,0:05:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.59,0:05:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Firstly, we've got to compare the names written here against the list of victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.87,0:05:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erm... {\alpha&HFF&}yes... I suppose you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.69,0:05:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erm... yes... {\alpha&HFF&}I suppose you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.19,0:05:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erm... yes... I suppose you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've won.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.53,0:05:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as planned!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.71,0:05:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm relinquishing all ownership of this notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.13,0:05:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ownership of this notebook now returns to Rem. {\alpha&HFF&}Correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:05:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ownership of this notebook now returns to Rem. Correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.26,0:05:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct. {\alpha&HFF&}Your point being?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct. Your point being?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, now give that notebook to Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.26,0:06:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The owner of this notebook is now Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.82,0:06:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuk, next, I want you to drop that notebook here, onto the ground of the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Well, guess it's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.46,0:06:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so the ownership returns to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.02,0:06:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the ownership has gone round in a circle; nothing has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there'll be a time when this will be of use.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the first notebook that I received from Ryuk...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm giving it back to you, and I want you to give it to Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.98,0:06:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.15,0:06:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rem, I'll need you to pass that to someone who has a reasonably high status, yet remains greedy for success.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who'll undoubtedly use the notebook to further those goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.89,0:07:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing this will guarantee Misa's release from imprisonment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.33,0:07:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she still hasn't been released after several years, kill me. {\alpha&HFF&}How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.06,0:07:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she still hasn't been released after several years, kill me. How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.17,0:07:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami Light, {\alpha&HFF&}what are you planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.65,0:07:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami Light, what are you planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all to save Misa. {\alpha&HFF&}Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.60,0:07:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all to save Misa. Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.38,0:07:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood... {\alpha&HFF&}if this will help Misa, I'll do as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood... if this will help Misa, I'll do as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, I'll manipulate the situation so, like Misa, I'll be detained and under 24-hour surveillance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.03,0:07:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While in detention, I'll relinquish all ownership of the Death Note and it'll erase any associated memories I've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.41,0:07:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During that time, the judging of criminals will recommence, and if that continues, at some stage, Ryuuzaki will be forced to release us both.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.94,0:08:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, with my memories gone, {\alpha&HFF&}I'm sure I'll attempt to catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.76,0:08:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, with my memories gone, I'm sure I'll attempt to catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just the type of person I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.70,0:08:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you plan to find the person Rem gives the notebook to before L can, and reclaim the notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly. {\alpha&HFF&}And I'll kill whoever has ownership of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.89,0:08:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly. And I'll kill whoever has ownership of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.40,0:08:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is one problem:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.12,0:08:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hold no ownership over that Death Note, your memories will only return as long as you're physically touching it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.09,0:08:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment you let go, all your memories will be erased once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.48,0:08:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to kill Higuchi without letting go of this notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.86,0:08:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way, the ownership will pass to me, and my memories won't disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I pull this four times with less than a second between each...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.40,0:08:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Success! {\alpha&HFF&}I knew I'd be wearing this at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Success! I knew I'd be wearing this at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.93,0:08:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old habits die hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.89,0:09:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-san, please escort Higuchi to the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.87,0:09:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-{\alpha&HFF&}Okay... understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay... {\alpha&HFF&}understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.04,0:09:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay... understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.59,0:09:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This notebook... {\alpha&HFF&}if analyzed scientifically, I wonder if we'd discover anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This notebook... if analyzed scientifically, {\alpha&HFF&}I wonder if we'd discover anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.28,0:09:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This notebook... if analyzed scientifically, I wonder if we'd discover anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.32,0:09:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun, that's not like you. {\alpha&HFF&}That thing is beyond science.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.39,0:09:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun, that's not like you. That thing is beyond science.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.29,0:09:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the longest 40 seconds of my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.99,0:10:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Higuchi! {\alpha&HFF&}Ryuuzaki! Higuchi is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.92,0:10:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Higuchi! Ryuuzaki! {\alpha&HFF&}Higuchi is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.49,0:10:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Higuchi! Ryuuzaki! Higuchi is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.60,0:10:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! {\alpha&HFF&}What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.65,0:10:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Higuchi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, father?! {\alpha&HFF&}If Higuchi dies now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.01,0:10:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, father?! If Higuchi dies now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-{\alpha&HFF&}This isn't possible... but I think he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This isn't possible... {\alpha&HFF&}but I think he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.66,0:10:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This isn't possible... but I think he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, {\alpha&HFF&}he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.45,0:10:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.98,0:10:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next, Ryuuzaki... {\alpha&HFF&}will be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.18,0:10:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next, Ryuuzaki... will be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.72,0:11:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"How to use"...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Those whose names are written in this notebook will die."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.80,0:11:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"This note will not take effect unless the writer has the person's face in their mind when they write his/her name."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Therefore, people sharing the same name will not be affected."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.27,0:11:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"If the cause of death is written within 40 seconds of writing the person's name, it will happen as it is written."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"If the cause of death is not specified, by default, the person will die of a heart attack"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.94,0:11:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Should a cause of death be specified, a further 6 minutes 40 seconds are granted to write any further details."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.39,0:11:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, in the "How to use"-section at the back, it states:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"If this notebook is made unusable via shredding, burning and so forth, all those who have touched the notebook will die."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.11,0:12:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! {\alpha&HFF&}Is that true, Aizawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.24,0:12:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Is that true, Aizawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, it's written right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.15,0:12:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt that while that rule exists, they won't destroy the notebook, and there's no danger of me losing my memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.69,0:12:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw.. that's just shit... why didn't you tell me this earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.58,0:12:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rem, I won't get in trouble with the old man for writing in fake rules, will I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.87,0:12:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there are no rules regarding that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.13,0:12:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright then. {\alpha&HFF&}But Light, I'm counting on you for more apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.44,0:12:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright then. But Light, I'm counting on you for more apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.95,0:12:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I shouldn't have said "I want to see the Shinigami too", and touched that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.10,0:12:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hadn't, you'd be the only one in the investigation not knowing what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.56,0:12:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I want to be on the same level as everyone else in this investigation. Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this final sentence...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.01,0:13:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"From the moment a new user writes a name into this notebook, they must continue to write names,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,each within 13 days of the last; otherwise, the user will die."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.48,0:13:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! {\alpha&HFF&}This means that both Light-kun and Misa-Misa are completely cleared!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.63,0:13:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! This means that both Light-kun and Misa-Misa are completely cleared!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun and Amane were imprisoned for over 50 days, and even now are under surveillance. {\alpha&HFF&}If either were Kira, they'd no longer be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun and Amane were imprisoned for over 50 days, and even now are under surveillance. If either were Kira, they'd no longer be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great news, isn't it, Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.69,0:13:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.07,0:13:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rem-san... {\alpha&HFF&}wasn't it? The white person over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.72,0:13:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rem-san... wasn't it? The white person over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ryuuzaki, that's rude! You can't go around calling them "white".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.09,0:13:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.98,0:13:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are other Death Notes in the human world, aren't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.21,0:13:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not sure. Maybe there are, maybe there aren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.59,0:13:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If other notebooks did exist, {\alpha&HFF&}would the rules be the same for all of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.07,0:13:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If other notebooks did exist, would the rules be the same for all of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use, Ryuuzaki. {\alpha&HFF&}There's no way that Rem will let you cast doubt upon these rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:14:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use, Ryuuzaki. There's no way that Rem will let you cast doubt upon these rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.05,0:14:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, they'd be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are many notebooks within the world of Shinigami, but the rules are all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those notebooks under human possession also share a common set of rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.00,0:14:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, the suspicions surrounding Light-kun and Amane have been cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.68,0:14:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to end their surveillance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.41,0:14:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right, it's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.85,0:14:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for everything up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.72,0:14:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.26,0:14:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the case is still far from solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.85,0:14:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although these handcuffs will be removed, I'll continue to investigate from here, if that's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.17,0:14:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now Misa and I are 100% clear of suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.88,0:15:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rules written by a Shinigami in a Death Note... {\alpha&HFF&}you'd have to believe them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.11,0:15:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rules written by a Shinigami in a Death Note... you'd have to believe them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.95,0:15:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to the fake rules I created, Ryuuzaki has nowhere to go from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.22,0:15:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand this Ryuuzaki: {\alpha&HFF&}in any world, rules are something that are made by the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.23,0:15:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand this Ryuuzaki: in any world, rules are something that are made by the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.99,0:15:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will bow down to the rules I've created.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.43,0:15:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You tried to oppose me, the new god of this world, and for your transgression, you will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.51,0:15:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light! Promise me that you'll text me every single day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.04,0:15:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that I finally have to part with Misa-Misa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, Matsuda, leave them alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.30,0:15:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya, Misa-Misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.05,0:15:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.16,0:15:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we can be seen on the security cameras, from this angle, they shouldn't be able to see my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, when you're certain that no one else is around, I want you to go to the place I'm about to tell you and dig up something for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light! Your memories have returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.26,0:16:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Misa will do good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.17,0:16:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, I remember! {\alpha&HFF&}Everything that happened back when I was using this notebook... You must have buried this notebook so that I'd remember too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.37,0:16:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, I remember! Everything that happened back when I was using this notebook... {\alpha&HFF&}You must have buried this notebook so that I'd remember too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.15,0:16:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, I remember! Everything that happened back when I was using this notebook... You must have buried this notebook so that I'd remember too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.67,0:16:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, if you're reading this, it's likely that your memory has been restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A letter from Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.49,0:16:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember a friend of mine, from Todai University, who introduced himself as "Ryuuga Hideki"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to write his real name in this notebook and bury him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.03,0:17:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, as soon as possible, burn this letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.20,0:17:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take only a few pages from the notebook, and re-bury the notebook itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next time you see me, touch me with a piece of paper from this notebook as naturally as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.01,0:17:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can obey me in all this... {\alpha&HFF&}I'll love you, forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can obey me in all this... I'll love you, forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,                              ...love you, forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.06,0:17:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.68,0:17:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. This is all Light's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.65,0:17:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For me to obtain this notebook and regain my memory... {\alpha&HFF&}and kill Ryuuga Hideki... Ryuuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For me to obtain this notebook and regain my memory... and kill Ryuuga Hideki... {\alpha&HFF&}Ryuuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.52,0:17:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For me to obtain this notebook and regain my memory... and kill Ryuuga Hideki... Ryuuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.60,0:17:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This should remove another obstacle for Light, and I'll have helped him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.54,0:17:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good, Light. {\alpha&HFF&}I can't remember his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.04,0:17:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good, Light. I can't remember his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.09,0:17:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to see tens, hundreds of names and lifespans every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can remember! {\alpha&HFF&}Stupid Misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.54,0:17:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can remember! Stupid Misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.02,0:18:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally! I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.57,0:18:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuk! It's so good to see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.98,0:18:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erm, sorry but... {\alpha&HFF&}being male and all that... that kinda makes me blush.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.32,0:18:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erm, sorry but... being male and all that... {\alpha&HFF&}that kinda makes me blush.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.18,0:18:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erm, sorry but... being male and all that... that kinda makes me blush.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.52,0:18:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light told me to bring it along.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.19,0:18:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Apples in the human world are... how d'ya say it? "Juicy"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.10,0:18:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, they're damned good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.31,0:18:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna try eating one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an apple from the world of Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.82,0:18:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't look very tasty...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.52,0:18:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.19,0:18:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, Ryuk. {\alpha&HFF&}I want to trade eyes with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.30,0:18:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, Ryuk. I want to trade eyes with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.77,0:18:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sand!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.62,0:18:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna make a deal, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.01,0:19:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You realize that you've already made a deal with Rem once, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your remaining lifespan has already been halved once; {\alpha&HFF&}you sure you wanna do it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.16,0:19:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your remaining lifespan has already been halved once; you sure you wanna do it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.16,0:19:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.77,0:19:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've completely forgotten the one name that I needed to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light will be mad at me unless I go and find it out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.10,0:19:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.43,0:19:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Misa-Misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor thing. We can't switch our cell phones on in here, so Misa-Misa has to come all the way here, just to see Light-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.68,0:19:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, hurry up and go see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.27,0:19:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't keep a lady waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.87,0:19:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuk! {\alpha&HFF&}Why is he with Misa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuk! Why is he with Misa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.70,0:20:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa's lifespan has halved again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.19,0:20:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely she didn't trade eyes with Ryuk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.68,0:20:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-{\alpha&HFF&}Light, I'm so sorry. I can't remember Ryuuga Hideki's name, no matter how hard I try!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.14,0:20:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Light, I'm so sorry. {\alpha&HFF&}I can't remember Ryuuga Hideki's name, no matter how hard I try!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Light, I'm so sorry. I can't remember Ryuuga Hideki's name, {\alpha&HFF&}no matter how hard I try!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.46,0:20:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Light, I'm so sorry. I can't remember Ryuuga Hideki's name, no matter how hard I try!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.46,0:20:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.10,0:20:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's a shame...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-{\alpha&HFF&}But I traded eyes with Ryuk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I traded eyes with Ryuk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all going according to plan, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! {\alpha&HFF&}That means your lifespan has...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.58,0:20:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! That means your lifespan has...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.36,0:20:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter. I want to help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.66,0:20:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, I want to be with you in an ideal world for as long as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.67,0:20:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the way I feel, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.22,0:20:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light! I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.60,0:21:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, let's build a new world together... {\alpha&HFF&}a world without criminals, filled only with kind-hearted people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.50,0:21:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, let's build a new world together... a world without criminals, filled only with kind-hearted people.
